{
  "video_id": "P9B8PmUR64U",
  "title": "What can we learn from shortcuts? | Tom Hulme",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12771.0,
      "end_time": 15180.0,
      "text": "When we&#39;re designing new products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15420.0,
      "end_time": 17320.0,
      "text": "services or businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17560.0,
      "end_time": 19574.0,
      "text": "the only time you&#39;ll know if they&#39;re any good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19598.0,
      "end_time": 21296.0,
      "text": "if the designs are good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21320.0,
      "end_time": 26550.0,
      "text": "is to see how they&#39;re used in the real world, in context."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26761.0,
      "end_time": 30695.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m reminded of that every time I walk past Highbury Fields"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30719.0,
      "end_time": 32159.0,
      "text": "in north London."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32183.0,
      "end_time": 33501.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s absolutely beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33525.0,
      "end_time": 35222.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a big open green space."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35246.0,
      "end_time": 37814.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s Georgian buildings around the side."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37838.0,
      "end_time": 40736.0,
      "text": "But then there&#39;s this mud trap that cuts across the middle."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41720.0,
      "end_time": 44844.0,
      "text": "People clearly don&#39;t want to walk all the way around the edge."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45196.0,
      "end_time": 47332.0,
      "text": "Instead, they want to take the shortcut,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47356.0,
      "end_time": 49812.0,
      "text": "and that shortcut is self-reinforcing."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50866.0,
      "end_time": 54162.0,
      "text": "Now, this shortcut is called a desire path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54186.0,
      "end_time": 56686.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s often the path of least resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56710.0,
      "end_time": 58430.0,
      "text": "I find them fascinating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58670.0,
      "end_time": 63532.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re often the point where design and user experience diverge."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64164.0,
      "end_time": 66170.0,
      "text": "Now at this point, I should apologize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66410.0,
      "end_time": 68913.0,
      "text": "because you guys are going to start seeing these everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68937.0,
      "end_time": 71599.0,
      "text": "But today, I&#39;m going to pick three I find interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71623.0,
      "end_time": 73734.0,
      "text": "and share what actually it reminds me"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73758.0,
      "end_time": 76566.0,
      "text": "about launching new products and services."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77137.0,
      "end_time": 80800.0,
      "text": "The first is in the capital city of Brazil -- Brasilia."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81203.0,
      "end_time": 83341.0,
      "text": "And it reminds me that sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83365.0,
      "end_time": 86493.0,
      "text": "you have to just focus on designing for a real need"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86517.0,
      "end_time": 87786.0,
      "text": "at low friction."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88251.0,
      "end_time": 89764.0,
      "text": "Now, Brasilia is fascinating."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89788.0,
      "end_time": 92929.0,
      "text": "It was designed by Niemeyer in the &#39;50s."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 92954.0,
      "end_time": 95161.0,
      "text": "It was the golden age of flying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95186.0,
      "end_time": 98450.0,
      "text": "so he laid it out like a plane, as you can see there."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 98474.0,
      "end_time": 99639.0,
      "text": "Slightly worryingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99663.0,
      "end_time": 103411.0,
      "text": "he put most of the important government buildings in the cockpit."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 103435.0,
      "end_time": 105882.0,
      "text": "But if you zoom in, in the very center of Brasilia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105906.0,
      "end_time": 108680.0,
      "text": "just where the point is there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108920.0,
      "end_time": 110492.0,
      "text": "you see it&#39;s littered with desire paths."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110973.0,
      "end_time": 113450.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re absolutely everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113700.0,
      "end_time": 115940.0,
      "text": "Now, they thought that they had future-proofed this design."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115964.0,
      "end_time": 118979.0,
      "text": "They thought in the future we wouldn&#39;t need to walk anywhere --"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119300.0,
      "end_time": 120551.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d be able to drive --"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120575.0,
      "end_time": 123532.0,
      "text": "so there was little need for walkways or pavements."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 124358.0,
      "end_time": 126691.0,
      "text": "But as you can see, there&#39;s a real need."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 127564.0,
      "end_time": 129386.0,
      "text": "These are very dangerous desire paths."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129410.0,
      "end_time": 131447.0,
      "text": "If we just pick one, in the middle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 131471.0,
      "end_time": 134878.0,
      "text": "you can see it crosses 15 lanes of traffic."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134902.0,
      "end_time": 136658.0,
      "text": "It won&#39;t surprise you guys"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 136682.0,
      "end_time": 140221.0,
      "text": "that Brasilia has five times the pedestrian accident rate"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140246.0,
      "end_time": 142124.0,
      "text": "of your average US city."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142968.0,
      "end_time": 144454.0,
      "text": "People are resourceful."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 144479.0,
      "end_time": 147513.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll always find the low-friction route"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 147537.0,
      "end_time": 149932.0,
      "text": "to save money, save time."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 150493.0,
      "end_time": 152476.0,
      "text": "Not all these desire paths are dangerous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 152500.0,
      "end_time": 155893.0,
      "text": "I was reminded flying here when I was in Heathrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 155917.0,
      "end_time": 158437.0,
      "text": "Many of us get frustrated when we&#39;re confronted"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 158461.0,
      "end_time": 161130.0,
      "text": "with the obligatory walk through duty-free."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 163240.0,
      "end_time": 164175.0,
      "text": "It was amazing to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164199.0,
      "end_time": 168334.0,
      "text": "how many people refused to take the long, meandering path to the left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 168358.0,
      "end_time": 170435.0,
      "text": "and just cut through to the right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170459.0,
      "end_time": 172180.0,
      "text": "cut through the desire path."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 172813.0,
      "end_time": 174521.0,
      "text": "The question that&#39;s interesting is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 174545.0,
      "end_time": 177734.0,
      "text": "What do designers think when they see our behavior here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178198.0,
      "end_time": 179989.0,
      "text": "Do they think we&#39;re stupid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 180130.0,
      "end_time": 181809.0,
      "text": "Do they think we&#39;re lazy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 182405.0,
      "end_time": 184957.0,
      "text": "Or do they accept that this is the only truth?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 184981.0,
      "end_time": 186739.0,
      "text": "This is their product."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 187134.0,
      "end_time": 189666.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re effectively co-designing their product."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 190540.0,
      "end_time": 195465.0,
      "text": "So our job is to design for real needs at low friction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 195490.0,
      "end_time": 198386.0,
      "text": "because if you don&#39;t, the customer will, anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 199238.0,
      "end_time": 201458.0,
      "text": "The second desire path I wanted to share"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 201482.0,
      "end_time": 203734.0,
      "text": "is at the University of California."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 203758.0,
      "end_time": 204910.0,
      "text": "And it reminds me"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 204934.0,
      "end_time": 208910.0,
      "text": "that sometimes the best way to come up with a great design"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 208116.0,
      "end_time": 209800.0,
      "text": "is just to launch it."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 210864.0,
      "end_time": 214738.0,
      "text": "Now, university campuses are fantastic for spotting desire paths."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 214762.0,
      "end_time": 218100.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s because students are always late and they&#39;re pretty smart."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 218124.0,
      "end_time": 219606.0,
      "text": "So they&#39;re dashing to lectures."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 219630.0,
      "end_time": 221722.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll always find the shortcut."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 222436.0,
      "end_time": 224506.0,
      "text": "And the designers here knew that."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 224530.0,
      "end_time": 226503.0,
      "text": "So they built the buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 226527.0,
      "end_time": 229440.0,
      "text": "and then they waited a few months for the paths to form."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 229830.0,
      "end_time": 231354.0,
      "text": "They then paved them."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 231378.0,
      "end_time": 232416.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 232441.0,
      "end_time": 234346.0,
      "text": "Incredibly smart approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 234719.0,
      "end_time": 237841.0,
      "text": "In fact, often, just launching the straw man of a service"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 237866.0,
      "end_time": 240700.0,
      "text": "can teach you what people really want."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 240667.0,
      "end_time": 244861.0,
      "text": "For example, Ayr Muir in Boston knew he wanted to open a restaurant."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 244885.0,
      "end_time": 246292.0,
      "text": "But where should it be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 246675.0,
      "end_time": 248236.0,
      "text": "What should the menu be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 248661.0,
      "end_time": 250150.0,
      "text": "He launched a service,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 250174.0,
      "end_time": 251860.0,
      "text": "in this case a food truck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 251884.0,
      "end_time": 254259.0,
      "text": "and he changed the location each day."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 254283.0,
      "end_time": 257827.0,
      "text": "He&#39;d write a different menu on the side in a whiteboard marker"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 257851.0,
      "end_time": 259762.0,
      "text": "to figure out what people wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 260218.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262637.0,
      "text": "He now has a chain of restaurants."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 262661.0,
      "end_time": 264692.0,
      "text": "So it can be incredibly efficient"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 264716.0,
      "end_time": 267481.0,
      "text": "to launch something to spot the desire paths."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 268232.0,
      "end_time": 271314.0,
      "text": "The third and final desire path I wanted to share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 271338.0,
      "end_time": 272961.0,
      "text": "is the UNIH."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 273594.0,
      "end_time": 275883.0,
      "text": "It reminds me that the world&#39;s in flux,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 275907.0,
      "end_time": 278207.0,
      "text": "and we have to respond to those changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 278770.0,
      "end_time": 280837.0,
      "text": "So as you&#39;ll guess, this is a hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 281337.0,
      "end_time": 284378.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve marked for you on the left the Oncology Department."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 284735.0,
      "end_time": 289830.0,
      "text": "The patients would usually stay in the hotels down on the bottom right."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 290300.0,
      "end_time": 292243.0,
      "text": "This was a patient-centered organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 292267.0,
      "end_time": 294895.0,
      "text": "so they laid on cars for their patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 295871.0,
      "end_time": 299263.0,
      "text": "But what they realized when they started offering chemotherapy"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 299287.0,
      "end_time": 302630.0,
      "text": "is the patients rarely wanted to get in cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 302880.0,
      "end_time": 305990.0,
      "text": "They were too nauseous, so they&#39;d walk back to their hotels."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 306140.0,
      "end_time": 308953.0,
      "text": "This desire path that you see diagonally, formed."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 309616.0,
      "end_time": 312133.0,
      "text": "The patients even called it \"The Chemo Trail.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 312930.0,
      "end_time": 314999.0,
      "text": "Now, when the hospital saw this originally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 315230.0,
      "end_time": 317917.0,
      "text": "they tried to lay turf back over it, ignore it."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 318744.0,
      "end_time": 321860.0,
      "text": "But after a while, they realized it was an important need"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 321884.0,
      "end_time": 323661.0,
      "text": "they were meeting for their patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 323685.0,
      "end_time": 324993.0,
      "text": "so they paved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 325170.0,
      "end_time": 328866.0,
      "text": "And I think our job is often to pave these emerging desire paths."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 328890.0,
      "end_time": 332150.0,
      "text": "If we look back at the one in North London again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 332400.0,
      "end_time": 334410.0,
      "text": "that desire path hasn&#39;t always been there."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 334856.0,
      "end_time": 336372.0,
      "text": "The reason it sprung up"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 336396.0,
      "end_time": 340494.0,
      "text": "is people were traveling to the mighty Arsenal Football Club stadium"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 340518.0,
      "end_time": 341669.0,
      "text": "on game days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 341693.0,
      "end_time": 344469.0,
      "text": "from the Underground station you see on the bottom right."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 344805.0,
      "end_time": 346104.0,
      "text": "So you see the desire path."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 346128.0,
      "end_time": 348942.0,
      "text": "If we just wind the clock back a few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 348966.0,
      "end_time": 351163.0,
      "text": "when the stadium was being constructed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 351187.0,
      "end_time": 352746.0,
      "text": "there is no desire path."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 353797.0,
      "end_time": 357943.0,
      "text": "So our job is to watch for these desire paths emerging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 358567.0,
      "end_time": 360331.0,
      "text": "and, where appropriate, pave them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 360975.0,
      "end_time": 362530.0,
      "text": "as someone did here."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 363191.0,
      "end_time": 364839.0,
      "text": "Someone installed a barrier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 366760.0,
      "end_time": 369296.0,
      "text": "people started walking across and round the bottom as you see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 369320.0,
      "end_time": 370518.0,
      "text": "and they paved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 370542.0,
      "end_time": 372121.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 372146.0,
      "end_time": 374534.0,
      "text": "But I think this is a wonderful reminder as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 374558.0,
      "end_time": 376409.0,
      "text": "that, actually, the world is in flux."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 376434.0,
      "end_time": 377656.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s constantly changing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 377680.0,
      "end_time": 379912.0,
      "text": "because if you look at the top of this image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 379936.0,
      "end_time": 381928.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s another desire path forming."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 383413.0,
      "end_time": 385943.0,
      "text": "So these three desire paths remind me"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 385967.0,
      "end_time": 389114.0,
      "text": "we need to design for real human needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 389579.0,
      "end_time": 392620.0,
      "text": "I think empathy for what your customers want"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 392860.0,
      "end_time": 395820.0,
      "text": "is probably the biggest leading indicator of business success."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 396315.0,
      "end_time": 397989.0,
      "text": "Design for real needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 398130.0,
      "end_time": 400417.0,
      "text": "and design them in low friction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 401155.0,
      "end_time": 403789.0,
      "text": "because if you don&#39;t offer them in low friction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 403814.0,
      "end_time": 406409.0,
      "text": "someone else will, often the customer."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 406875.0,
      "end_time": 411350.0,
      "text": "Secondly, often the best way to learn what people really want"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 411590.0,
      "end_time": 412923.0,
      "text": "is to launch your service."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 412947.0,
      "end_time": 415727.0,
      "text": "The answer is rarely inside the building."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 415751.0,
      "end_time": 418224.0,
      "text": "Get out there and see what people really want."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 418706.0,
      "end_time": 421149.0,
      "text": "And finally, in part because of technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 421173.0,
      "end_time": 423986.0,
      "text": "the world is incredibly flux at the moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 424100.0,
      "end_time": 425969.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s changing constantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 425993.0,
      "end_time": 429238.0,
      "text": "These desire paths are going to spring up faster than ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 429730.0,
      "end_time": 432677.0,
      "text": "Our job is to pick the appropriate ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 432701.0,
      "end_time": 433946.0,
      "text": "and pave over them."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 434572.0,
      "end_time": 435723.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 435747.0,
      "end_time": 439712.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}